stration of gene therapy to the contralateral eye in subjects who had previously had received unilateral gene therapy. We have demonstrated a heretofore unappreciated plasticity of the central nervous system with respect to restoration of vision.</p>\n</div>',NULL,NULL,1,1,2,0,0,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',14,18);
